<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yil ceyvittāṉ Irāyar Alaṅkārapiriyaṉ Āṉa tiruoṟṟiūraṉ Ivaṉe Ippaṭāri
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṇṇūṟu Ivai kumārakaṇattā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">bhai</hi>yār paṭārikaḷukku kūṟiṭukiṉṟa po 
<lb n="3" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> kāvaṉ vaḻutiyūr tāṉapa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Oru māvum Iraṇ
<lb n="4" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> māvum muṉṟām <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṟavaḻi paṭa<unclear>kā</unclear>maka
<lb n="5" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ṅku pāṭupāṭe tiruamutupuṟam tiruviḻā Eḻunāḷaikkum tiruvu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yum Ivvūr <hi rend="grantha">madhyasta</hi>ṉ Irāyar Alaṅkārapiriyaṉāyiṉa tiruvoṟ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <note n="543-1">Damaged.</note>
